{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Right off the bat, you will be working on a surveillance      assignment. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>However, this is not just a surveillance assignment. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>If something strange happens while you are monitoring, you will be asked to report it as an &quot;Anomaly&quot;.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Monitoring All Night&quot; is a horror-style game with no jump scares, so even those who are not good at horror can play with confidence. Report any unusual events appropriately and survive until the end of your shift! And watch out for the aliens!\ud83d\udc7d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are three locations to work from: Apartment, The Backrooms, and Asylum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are three shifts: short from 0:00 to 2:00, middle from 0:00 to 4:00, and long from 0:00 to 6:00, plus the highly challenging Nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you clear Nightmare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Aliens are often reported before dawn! Be careful when working long hours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Apartment - Living</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras/Apartment_Living.png?t=1738338136\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Backrooms - Corridor<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras/Backrooms_Corridor.png?t=1738338136\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"